## Summary
This documentation explains how to build, analyze, and utilize predictions in Amplitude Activation to segment users based on their likelihood to perform future actions. It covers creating predictions from starting cohorts, analyzing model performance through feature importance metrics, and converting predictions into actionable predictive cohorts for targeting and analysis.

